Are you OK,brother?

3
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:25,636
brother?

4
00:00:26,582 --> 00:00:27,472
He'll be OK?

5
00:00:27,659 --> 00:00:30,143
No worries.
His surgery went well.

6
00:00:32,710 --> 00:00:33,592
Yoko...

7
00:00:34,225 --> 00:00:34,905
Hello?

8
00:00:35,780 --> 00:00:37,186
Oh,Chikako

9
00:00:37,913 --> 00:00:39,163
What happened about Mitsuharu?

10
00:00:39,928 --> 00:00:44,897
I'm alone now.
My brother is saying something on his own.

11
00:00:45,100 --> 00:00:46,366
I feel worry

12
00:00:47,954 --> 00:00:50,517
He keeps saying about Yoko

13
00:00:51,431 --> 00:00:53,173
The nurse says he's fine

14
00:00:53,431 --> 00:00:56,790
The nurse says he's regaining his memory in his dreams.

15
00:00:57,509 --> 00:00:59,564
I got relieved

16
00:00:59,759 --> 00:01:02,399
Can you see him again?

17
00:01:02,649 --> 00:01:04,423
I would like to see him

18
00:01:05,235 --> 00:01:05,876
But...

19
00:01:06,407 --> 00:01:13,064
Doctors thought the best way to cure his amnesia was to see someone who was around at the time.

20
00:01:13,911 --> 00:01:17,851
That's why I want you to come visit him

21
00:01:18,577 --> 00:01:20,552
OK?
Good night

22
00:01:27,662 --> 00:01:29,771
Did you get a call?

23
00:01:30,485 --> 00:01:31,523
No...

24
00:01:31,903 --> 00:01:34,436
Shinji hasn't come back yet,right?

25
00:01:34,597 --> 00:01:35,200
Not yet

26
00:01:35,438 --> 00:01:39,921
I really can't believe your husband hasn't come home yet.

27
00:01:45,179 --> 00:01:49,331
This is a 10,000 yen necklace.
Do you like it?

28
00:02:12,112 --> 00:02:19,277
<i>AT THE SIDE OF THE BRIDGE (Episode 2)</i>

29
00:03:02,058 --> 00:03:03,219
Yoko

30
00:03:05,551 --> 00:03:07,862
I was dreaming of you all the way

31
00:03:08,755 --> 00:03:10,284
Mitsuharu

32
00:03:11,252 --> 00:03:20,816
You and I were talking among beautiful flowers

33
00:03:22,869 --> 00:03:24,253
I had such a dream

34
00:03:24,521 --> 00:03:29,409
We used to talk in flowers

35
00:03:32,951 --> 00:03:37,114
Then you looked me in the eye and said...

36
00:03:38,565 --> 00:03:41,868
You are in my eyes

37
00:03:42,242 --> 00:03:44,564
You are in my eyes too

38
00:03:45,635 --> 00:03:49,686
I love you, Yoko

39
00:03:50,166 --> 00:03:51,471
Mitsuharu

40
00:03:54,385 --> 00:03:55,903
Yes, I know that

41
00:03:56,383 --> 00:03:58,102
Did you remember it?

42
00:03:58,797 --> 00:04:02,859
We went skiing in Shinshu together.

43
00:04:10,154 --> 00:04:11,850
Let's get married,Yoko

44
00:04:12,810 --> 00:04:14,540
as soon as we graduate

45
00:04:16,314 --> 00:04:20,053
I'll make you happy

46
00:04:24,236 --> 00:04:30,787
I feel like my memory is slowly coming back but...

47
00:04:31,368 --> 00:04:34,526
Don't worry.
You'll get back soon

48
00:04:35,296 --> 00:04:39,337
I only remember that I love you

49
00:04:41,535 --> 00:04:43,276
Mitsuharu

50
00:04:44,623 --> 00:04:50,940
I only remember that I love you

51
00:04:58,312 --> 00:05:05,801
After I graduated from school and got a job at my sister's company, my father fell ill and I had to return to Kyushu.

52
00:05:07,082 --> 00:05:11,580
You came to see me off at Sukiyabashi

53
00:05:12,012 --> 00:05:14,847
Yes,that's right

54
00:05:15,935 --> 00:05:18,636
I was student at the time

55
00:05:20,466 --> 00:05:26,437
He told me that he would pick me up after finishing school in half a year.

56
00:05:29,626 --> 00:05:32,260
I feel like my memory is slowly coming back

57
00:05:32,930 --> 00:05:37,640
But Your brother opposed our marriage.

58
00:05:38,030 --> 00:05:42,606
I was in Kyushu and didn't know that

59
00:05:42,729 --> 00:05:46,948
I wrote a letter to let you know that and that happened

60
00:05:53,151 --> 00:05:55,818
Are you OK?

61
00:05:55,997 --> 00:05:58,664
Doctor!

62
00:06:01,486 --> 00:06:04,522
I am an architectural engineer

63
00:06:06,854 --> 00:06:07,836
Doctor!

64
00:06:08,205 --> 00:06:10,247
Don't worry

65
00:06:11,586 --> 00:06:12,926
Yoko

66
00:06:13,216 --> 00:06:17,312
I was very confused for half a year

67
00:06:18,584 --> 00:06:22,022
My father got better, so I went back to Tokyo.

68
00:06:22,613 --> 00:06:24,031
I wanted to see you

69
00:06:29,756 --> 00:06:30,705
Mitsuharu

70
00:06:31,408 --> 00:06:35,459
I am not yet able to walk alone

71
00:06:37,297 --> 00:06:39,585
I'm not what Mitsuharu Sugano used to be

72
00:06:41,951 --> 00:06:43,580
Look what my hands are

73
00:06:44,384 --> 00:06:45,935
Look what my legs are

74
00:06:46,237 --> 00:06:48,949
I changed myself

75
00:06:49,060 --> 00:06:50,891
I can't believe it

76
00:06:51,696 --> 00:06:55,569
if you have any reason,tell me honestly

77
00:07:09,281 --> 00:07:11,357
I regret telling you that

78
00:07:13,864 --> 00:07:14,712
Yeah

79
00:07:16,699 --> 00:07:22,648
I injured my right hand and thought I could no longer design.

80
00:07:30,222 --> 00:07:32,543
Sorry.
Did I bother you?

81
00:07:33,023 --> 00:07:34,552
No...

82
00:07:37,793 --> 00:07:42,770
Toki encouraged me all the way

83
00:07:45,237 --> 00:07:49,590
She was my neighbor in the same apartment and always took care of me.

84
00:07:49,634 --> 00:07:53,630
These croquettes smell so good that I bought a lot.

85
00:07:53,857 --> 00:07:55,621
Toki also loved you?

86
00:07:57,340 --> 00:08:01,849
No... I had nothing to do with her

87
00:08:02,228 --> 00:08:09,192
But I couldn't believe it until I heard about her

88
00:08:09,985 --> 00:08:14,449
I found that out when you came to Hokkaido.

89
00:08:16,320 --> 00:08:19,936
Hokkaido.

90
00:08:21,610 --> 00:08:29,077
I was always struggling to forget you then.

91
00:09:10,611 --> 00:09:15,656
I heard you had an arranged marriage.

92
00:09:16,319 --> 00:09:18,216
My brother cheated on me

93
00:09:19,042 --> 00:09:24,321
When Ms. Toki told me about you, I went to see you.
Fujikawa and Aya saw me off

94
00:09:24,500 --> 00:09:26,386
Good luck

95
00:09:48,029 --> 00:09:49,301
Yoko

96
00:10:02,419 --> 00:10:03,992
Mitsuharu

97
00:10:07,999 --> 00:10:12,151
I lost my happiness

98
00:10:13,400 --> 00:10:15,186
because of Nobu

99
00:10:15,666 --> 00:10:18,825
This is his watch, you know?

100
00:10:21,012 --> 00:10:25,108
He left this in my bed this morning

101
00:10:25,599 --> 00:10:27,798
I can't believe it

102
00:10:33,645 --> 00:10:34,750
Yoko

103
00:10:35,163 --> 00:10:36,078
Hold on

104
00:10:36,591 --> 00:10:37,785
I feel sorry about you

105
00:10:39,683 --> 00:10:41,022
Do you blame me?

106
00:10:41,401 --> 00:10:44,605
I was just being honest.

107
00:10:45,040 --> 00:10:50,006
I blamed her too much

108
00:10:50,341 --> 00:10:52,674
I was too selfish at that time

109
00:10:53,455 --> 00:10:56,926
He broke our relationship

110
00:10:58,444 --> 00:11:01,279
he broke our relationship

111
00:11:01,747 --> 00:11:05,486
Please die with me

112
00:11:05,943 --> 00:11:07,160
Calm down

113
00:11:07,562 --> 00:11:10,609
I'll go to die if you don't like

114
00:11:10,709 --> 00:11:12,406
Hold on!

115
00:11:15,430 --> 00:11:20,040
You fell off a cliff and you lost your memory.

116
00:11:20,464 --> 00:11:23,957
I can't remember anything from it

117
00:11:23,982 --> 00:11:26,993
Don't push yourself too hard

118
00:11:27,477 --> 00:11:30,669
You just had surgery

119
00:11:34,174 --> 00:11:39,810
His memory has fully returned.
But some are still missing

120
00:11:40,357 --> 00:11:42,946
I worry about it

121
00:11:42,971 --> 00:11:45,100
Can it be unrecoverable?

122
00:11:46,223 --> 00:11:50,118
He doesn't know me at all?

123
00:11:51,491 --> 00:11:52,485
No way

124
00:11:52,510 --> 00:12:00,487
Sometimes people can't remember even if they try

125
00:12:01,021 --> 00:12:06,055
I think he will remember if something happens

126
00:12:07,450 --> 00:12:10,865
So he needs your help

127
00:12:11,523 --> 00:12:12,896
Can you see him often?

128
00:12:14,526 --> 00:12:15,787
I would try

129
00:12:21,283 --> 00:12:25,501
I knew immediately what this was when I received this from Mr. Fujikawa.

130
00:12:26,026 --> 00:12:27,801
He told me this was my work

131
00:12:28,693 --> 00:12:33,783
I also remember that I was in the middle of designing this

132
00:12:35,033 --> 00:12:38,448
That's good what you remember

133
00:12:41,213 --> 00:12:42,798
But not all

134
00:12:44,438 --> 00:12:45,287
YOKO

135
00:12:46,693 --> 00:12:49,885
You and I parted like that in Hokkaido.

136
00:12:51,533 --> 00:12:53,118
It's been more than a year

137
00:12:56,187 --> 00:13:03,620
I always think of you in this bed

138
00:13:06,041 --> 00:13:08,887
I'm wondering how you're spending the year at that time

139
00:13:11,811 --> 00:13:14,054
Tell me what you think

140
00:13:15,300 --> 00:13:18,525
Why Fujikawa doesn't want to talk about you?

141
00:13:19,775 --> 00:13:21,003
I want to know that

142
00:13:21,818 --> 00:13:24,508
Please tell me everything you know

143
00:13:27,659 --> 00:13:31,677
I met Mitsuharu all the time

144
00:13:33,597 --> 00:13:38,463
I visited him when I came to Tokyo

145
00:13:38,753 --> 00:13:43,842
I went with him to Sukiyabashi and your apartment in Gotanda.

146
00:13:44,634 --> 00:13:51,788
I asked you to remember me, but at that time your memory did not return.

147
00:13:51,799 --> 00:13:52,704
Hold on

148
00:13:53,652 --> 00:13:56,331
You guys visited my apartment?

149
00:14:00,927 --> 00:14:04,732
Yeah, that was my room

150
00:14:06,373 --> 00:14:11,362
I'm Yasuo Tateno.
People call me any way

151
00:14:12,225 --> 00:14:18,329
But I don't know what they call me.
I don't even know what name is Mitsuharu

152
00:14:21,080 --> 00:14:24,384
Who are you?
And why you are here?

153
00:14:24,563 --> 00:14:30,779
I'm wife of Sawano.
I'm here for visiting you

154
00:15:12,380 --> 00:15:17,145
I thought Mitsuharu was died

155
00:15:23,879 --> 00:15:28,388
After returning from Hokkaido, I did as my brother said.

156
00:15:29,854 --> 00:15:31,115
I see

157
00:15:32,466 --> 00:15:43,020
I got married with Sawano..
So we can't see each other anymore

158
00:15:45,029 --> 00:15:46,659
Yoko

159
00:15:50,375 --> 00:15:52,786
Take care of your health

160
00:15:55,907 --> 00:15:57,101
Sis

161
00:17:47,536 --> 00:17:48,384
Welcome back

162
00:17:48,473 --> 00:17:50,002
I'm home

163
00:17:55,423 --> 00:17:56,639
Yoko

164
00:17:56,862 --> 00:17:58,034
I'm back now

165
00:17:58,347 --> 00:18:01,327
You were always with Omori's older brother, weren't you?

166
00:18:01,352 --> 00:18:02,060
Yes

167
00:18:02,171 --> 00:18:03,767
His sister was at his house?

168
00:18:04,783 --> 00:18:05,452
Yes

169
00:18:05,709 --> 00:18:07,863
I see.
Come with me

170
00:18:15,233 --> 00:18:16,226
Yoko

171
00:18:18,112 --> 00:18:20,936
Where have you been?
You cheated me

172
00:18:25,775 --> 00:18:27,963
Say sorry to her

173
00:18:28,052 --> 00:18:30,306
I won't forgive her

174
00:18:30,451 --> 00:18:31,445
Yoko

175
00:18:31,470 --> 00:18:32,360
I know where have you been

176
00:18:32,996 --> 00:18:34,949
I knew you visited him at the hospital

177
00:18:35,905 --> 00:18:37,959
Are you sure,Yoko?

178
00:18:37,984 --> 00:18:43,550
she tricked me into going to see him

179
00:18:44,789 --> 00:18:46,642
I didn't mean that

180
00:18:47,093 --> 00:18:48,745
Why did you trick me?

181
00:18:50,218 --> 00:18:53,187
I feel bad for lying to you

182
00:18:53,801 --> 00:18:57,149
I thought I shouldn't be honest

183
00:18:57,569 --> 00:19:02,402
You are the wife of Shinsuke.
You can't see other men

184
00:19:02,893 --> 00:19:05,114
I'm sorry

185
00:19:05,292 --> 00:19:07,863
I'll teach her.
Please forgive her

186
00:19:07,888 --> 00:19:11,168
I won't forgive her,
So I asked you pick her up

187
00:19:14,203 --> 00:19:21,334
Please talk to her and Kenjiro.
I'll discuss about her with Shinsuke too

188
00:19:32,528 --> 00:19:37,595
Hi Sugano.
You know who I am?

189
00:19:38,767 --> 00:19:40,006
What's wrong,Chikako?

190
00:19:40,129 --> 00:19:44,693
You know my name?
Who told you?

191
00:19:45,485 --> 00:19:48,364
No worried.
My memory got return

192
00:19:48,766 --> 00:19:50,529
Really?

193
00:19:52,002 --> 00:19:54,836
I know you are 13 years old

194
00:19:55,094 --> 00:19:55,641
And?

195
00:19:56,578 --> 00:19:57,639
I know you like Steamed bread

196
00:19:58,018 --> 00:19:59,380
Yes,and?

197
00:19:59,949 --> 00:20:03,431
you like playing the harmonica

198
00:20:03,456 --> 00:20:06,378
Yes but not very good

199
00:20:08,225 --> 00:20:11,684
How's him,Chikako?

200
00:20:13,839 --> 00:20:18,493
Her parents died and she was raised by relatives.

201
00:20:19,882 --> 00:20:22,895
I drowned in the river and was saved by the relative.

202
00:20:23,409 --> 00:20:25,083
That's good you remember it

203
00:20:26,177 --> 00:20:29,436
I was worried about his memory

204
00:20:30,359 --> 00:20:32,469
Don't cry

205
00:20:32,871 --> 00:20:36,788
I haven't forgotten to find your grandfather

206
00:20:38,931 --> 00:20:42,357
I'm glad if you are with me even if we can't find my grand father

207
00:20:44,409 --> 00:20:51,675
I'm glad you get better.
Get well soon and leave the hospital

208
00:20:53,036 --> 00:20:56,251
Mr. Imura was worried about his work.

209
00:20:57,757 --> 00:21:06,942
Mr. Imura says he will be able to leave the hospital in a few days.
Will Mitsuharu Sugano be able to work immediately after being discharged from the hospital?

210
00:21:07,650 --> 00:21:10,552
He needs some rest

211
00:21:11,277 --> 00:21:16,132
if he needs a month rest

212
00:21:16,480 --> 00:21:19,526
If so, the design will be delayed.

213
00:21:20,062 --> 00:21:26,078
Our office will work with you on that and try to get it done as soon as possible.

214
00:21:27,647 --> 00:21:34,756
He has a brain disorder, so I'm worried about putting him in charge of this design.

215
00:21:34,991 --> 00:21:40,582
I wanted to build a building with a new feel, so I recommended Mr. Sugano.

216
00:21:41,308 --> 00:21:44,856
I will judge whether he is in charge of this work.

217
00:21:45,459 --> 00:21:46,888
What do you think?

218
00:21:47,078 --> 00:21:53,852
You're right. but it'll be inconvenienced if this work delay

219
00:21:59,267 --> 00:22:02,292
You work so hard

220
00:22:02,750 --> 00:22:07,370
No worries.
I'm happy to work

221
00:22:08,202 --> 00:22:10,993
I would like to see the building you designed

222
00:22:18,217 --> 00:22:20,527
What's wrong?

223
00:22:20,728 --> 00:22:22,926
Sugano will be discharged from the hospital tomorrow.

224
00:22:23,328 --> 00:22:25,917
I see.
He'll stay here?

225
00:22:25,942 --> 00:22:30,237
Yes.
Fujikawa visited me and asked me to clean the room

226
00:22:30,538 --> 00:22:33,295
She's so cheeky

227
00:22:37,083 --> 00:22:39,081
You're in a lot of trouble.

228
00:22:40,085 --> 00:22:40,476
Eh?

229
00:22:40,755 --> 00:22:45,632
Mr. Fujikawa said that even if he leaves the hospital, he won't worry as long as he stays here.

230
00:22:47,641 --> 00:22:50,040
He know nothing about us

231
00:22:53,333 --> 00:22:56,447
I want to go back to my hometown

232
00:22:56,472 --> 00:22:57,775
Why?

233
00:23:00,420 --> 00:23:05,822
I'm really sorry that Yoko caused you trouble.

234
00:23:05,847 --> 00:23:08,266
I'm not upset about it

235
00:23:09,244 --> 00:23:13,463
I'm here because our president was worried about you.

236
00:23:14,490 --> 00:23:16,331
Sorry for the inconvenience.

237
00:23:16,711 --> 00:23:18,050
I want sweets

238
00:23:18,217 --> 00:23:21,097
I'll give you later.
Go outside and play

239
00:23:22,233 --> 00:23:24,209
you apologize to her

240
00:23:27,887 --> 00:23:31,575
I'm sorry I lied to you

241
00:23:32,208 --> 00:23:35,466
But it can't be helped

242
00:23:39,876 --> 00:23:41,563
Please understand me

243
00:23:42,134 --> 00:23:43,438
What should I understand?

244
00:23:44,173 --> 00:23:48,946
The doctor told me to come to him to cure his disease.

245
00:23:49,345 --> 00:23:51,852
Don't get me wrong

246
00:23:52,040 --> 00:23:54,813
He already know about it

247
00:23:54,907 --> 00:23:59,407
But I think it would be very sad to take his job away from him.

248
00:23:59,571 --> 00:24:00,329
Job?

249
00:24:01,001 --> 00:24:01,977
What the hell?

250
00:24:02,306 --> 00:24:03,001
Yoko

251
00:24:03,056 --> 00:24:06,204
I think it's very sad that they won't let him design the building.

252
00:24:07,012 --> 00:24:09,255
I hope you understand about my feeling

253
00:24:10,255 --> 00:24:11,098
Miura

254
00:24:12,348 --> 00:24:16,161
The company has not yet made that decision.
What the hell?

255
00:24:16,637 --> 00:24:19,473
I'm sorry but you should scold her

256
00:24:20,512 --> 00:24:24,434
You have nothing to do with the Sugano now

257
00:24:24,695 --> 00:24:26,063
You want me to understand that?

258
00:24:27,406 --> 00:24:32,914
You have nothing to do with the Sugano now.
Why you care about him?

259
00:24:34,039 --> 00:24:35,594
He's saying right

260
00:24:38,071 --> 00:24:41,242
You can't go home unless you forget him

261
00:24:41,852 --> 00:24:42,461
I'm leaving now

262
00:24:42,727 --> 00:24:43,875
You should apologize to him.

263
00:24:44,227 --> 00:24:44,922
Miura

264
00:24:45,313 --> 00:24:46,414
Leave her alone

265
00:24:48,248 --> 00:24:48,904
Boss

266
00:24:50,474 --> 00:24:52,169
I am very sorry today

267
00:24:52,482 --> 00:24:54,927
What the hell?

268
00:24:55,857 --> 00:24:57,537
I am very sorry today

269
00:25:05,857 --> 00:25:07,865
why did you argue with him?

270
00:25:08,381 --> 00:25:10,013
He came to pick you up

271
00:25:10,294 --> 00:25:13,794
I wanted him to understand my feelings

