550
00:50:41,575 --> 00:50:43,104
It's the time

551
00:50:43,406 --> 00:50:46,486
I can't go

552
00:50:46,776 --> 00:50:50,850
You've failed in divorce mediation, and now you're going to a divorce trial, right?

553
00:50:51,564 --> 00:50:56,654
I can't help you.
I don't think you can solve it by yourself

554
00:50:57,870 --> 00:51:00,415
I don't know what to do too

555
00:51:02,078 --> 00:51:04,600
It is my responsibility to marry with Sawano

556
00:51:05,325 --> 00:51:09,042
I said good bye to Mitsuharu in Kyushu

557
00:51:11,002 --> 00:51:13,356
I will be patient as my divorce is finalized.

558
00:51:15,488 --> 00:51:16,973
It can't be helped

559
00:51:18,446 --> 00:51:22,285
Keep this story a secret from him

560
00:51:24,138 --> 00:51:28,189
I find it painful for her to lie to him

561
00:51:29,692 --> 00:51:31,009
I'm sorry

562
00:51:38,486 --> 00:51:41,410
Are you Sawano's wife from Toyo Light Metal?

563
00:51:43,105 --> 00:51:43,752
Yes

564
00:51:44,087 --> 00:51:45,795
I see

565
00:51:47,513 --> 00:51:50,717
Do you know about him?

566
00:51:50,772 --> 00:51:53,306
He is a client of ours and I have met him a few times.

567
00:51:54,318 --> 00:51:55,367
Thanks

568
00:52:00,891 --> 00:52:04,039
he is a very good lawyer

569
00:52:04,418 --> 00:52:06,070
Don't make me laugh

570
00:52:06,148 --> 00:52:07,387
Am I bothering you?

571
00:52:07,412 --> 00:52:09,820
It's OK.
I can't be loud

572
00:52:10,166 --> 00:52:14,682
Do we settle in district court?

573
00:52:14,917 --> 00:52:15,464
Yes

574
00:52:15,587 --> 00:52:18,031
I will support you

575
00:52:18,265 --> 00:52:20,654
Can we pay in installments?

576
00:52:21,123 --> 00:52:24,225
Ok that'll be fine

577
00:52:24,303 --> 00:52:26,234
I hope my own body recovers.

578
00:52:26,259 --> 00:52:29,214
your appendix will heal soon

579
00:52:29,414 --> 00:52:32,015
You'll get well soon

580
00:52:32,040 --> 00:52:35,196
Please take care of me.
I'm old fart

581
00:52:36,056 --> 00:52:38,198
You're still young

582
00:52:38,377 --> 00:52:41,245
you are good at flattery

583
00:52:42,741 --> 00:52:44,147
Bros

584
00:52:48,518 --> 00:52:50,326
You've been raised

585
00:52:53,507 --> 00:52:55,080
What's wrong?

586
00:52:55,683 --> 00:52:57,312
I just greet you

587
00:53:00,645 --> 00:53:02,665
I tell you before I forget

588
00:53:04,048 --> 00:53:04,740
What?

589
00:53:05,053 --> 00:53:09,562
Toki told me if you ask me about Yoko

590
00:53:09,663 --> 00:53:10,623
Then?

591
00:53:10,980 --> 00:53:16,739
She told me to tell you she is fine.

592
00:53:17,977 --> 00:53:19,350
That's good if she is happy

593
00:53:20,975 --> 00:53:22,381
Do you worry about her?

594
00:53:22,783 --> 00:53:24,077
Yes

595
00:53:25,327 --> 00:53:28,195
You're already adult

596
00:53:28,396 --> 00:53:29,736
Toki is fine?

597
00:53:29,761 --> 00:53:33,653
She's busy.
The patient she is in charge of now is a lawyer.

598
00:53:33,694 --> 00:53:35,870
she said it was convenient

599
00:53:36,417 --> 00:53:37,488
Why?

600
00:53:39,107 --> 00:53:43,035
Well...she's studying law

601
00:53:43,503 --> 00:53:44,307
Really?

602
00:53:47,153 --> 00:53:50,211
I can't believe what you say

603
00:53:53,934 --> 00:54:00,697
We will now begin deliberations on the divorce of Yoko Sawano and Shinsuke Sawano.

604
00:54:01,680 --> 00:54:03,421
where is the plaintiff's attorney?

605
00:54:03,599 --> 00:54:04,470
Well

606
00:54:04,715 --> 00:54:06,189
What's wrong?

607
00:54:11,869 --> 00:54:13,432
Sorry

608
00:54:16,255 --> 00:54:18,130
Sorry I'm late

609
00:54:19,472 --> 00:54:22,396
You should be prepared to substantiate.

610
00:54:23,043 --> 00:54:24,796
Wait a min

611
00:54:32,605 --> 00:54:37,214
I will slightly change the purpose and cause of the divorce request.

612
00:54:37,515 --> 00:54:42,080
In short,we will claim 1 million yen from him as compensation.

613
00:54:43,341 --> 00:54:45,439
Yoko..you are so mean

614
00:54:47,828 --> 00:54:49,111
Sensei

615
00:54:49,591 --> 00:54:51,388
Leave it to me.
This is the way to win the case

616
00:54:56,020 --> 00:54:58,754
Yoko

617
00:54:59,744 --> 00:55:04,264
I think it's a very terrible way to claim alimony from him.

618
00:55:04,365 --> 00:55:06,697
You should speak up on the witness stand it

619
00:55:06,954 --> 00:55:07,735
I will

620
00:55:07,981 --> 00:55:13,327
Thanks.
Because you the judge will know what kind of mother-in-law you are.

621
00:55:17,342 --> 00:55:19,436
you should have divorced her earlier

622
00:55:19,960 --> 00:55:21,975
You were also concerned about other people's eyes and opposed the divorce.

623
00:55:22,170 --> 00:55:24,038
Don't get argue

624
00:55:24,409 --> 00:55:26,057
What do you think?

625
00:55:26,354 --> 00:55:28,245
No worries.
Leave it to me

626
00:55:34,384 --> 00:55:35,080
Yoko

627
00:55:38,314 --> 00:55:42,564
I consulted with the president.
You have been asked to leave this company.

628
00:55:42,955 --> 00:55:44,345
Eh? Why?

629
00:55:44,845 --> 00:55:47,244
It's a problem with Sawano's house, isn't it?

630
00:55:47,853 --> 00:55:49,040
That's so mean

631
00:55:49,681 --> 00:55:55,587
This company does business with our company.
It is not convenient for us to have you working for us.

632
00:55:57,626 --> 00:56:01,220
Are you sure?
I'm not allowed to work here?

633
00:56:02,673 --> 00:56:06,985
Your brother said you wanted to be with Sawano-san again.

634
00:56:07,454 --> 00:56:08,743
That's not true

635
00:56:09,751 --> 00:56:13,361
I wanted to divorce him, so I went to court.

636
00:56:13,939 --> 00:56:16,400
I see.
Hold on

637
00:56:17,079 --> 00:56:20,720
Niimuera.
That's what I thought

638
00:56:23,095 --> 00:56:26,986
The person I hired is Yoko.
Not Sawano's wife

639
00:56:28,072 --> 00:56:30,220
So forget this issue

640
00:56:31,180 --> 00:56:35,157
Are you sure?
May I report this to the manager?

641
00:56:36,227 --> 00:56:37,977
we also have a deal

642
00:56:38,446 --> 00:56:44,524
you are a very big company.
I can't believe you would do something like that, so I'll call your president and see.

643
00:56:44,558 --> 00:56:46,636
Hold on.
You don't have to

644
00:56:50,393 --> 00:56:53,393
The president of your company is a woman, so you seem to understand how women feel.

645
00:56:53,534 --> 00:56:54,542
It might be so

646
00:56:54,800 --> 00:56:57,956
That's good she is nice person

647
00:56:58,620 --> 00:56:59,659
We're back

648
00:57:08,381 --> 00:57:09,702
Where did you arrived?

649
00:57:10,556 --> 00:57:12,619
Sis, he is....

650
00:57:13,228 --> 00:57:16,424
I'm here because I want to talk to you

651
00:57:16,791 --> 00:57:20,174
I see.
I invited her for dinner

652
00:57:22,107 --> 00:57:23,420
Come in,Yoko

653
00:57:32,637 --> 00:57:35,621
It's been a age,Yoko

654
00:57:41,168 --> 00:57:46,973
Sorry for the unexpected visit.

655
00:57:47,543 --> 00:57:51,168
he is going abroad

656
00:57:51,653 --> 00:57:52,121
Eh?

657
00:57:52,231 --> 00:57:55,293
To Ka...what name is it

658
00:57:56,918 --> 00:58:01,551
At the request of Professor Imura, I decided to go to Cambodia.

659
00:58:01,957 --> 00:58:03,293
I'll go for him

660
00:58:04,114 --> 00:58:06,348
Where will you depart?

661
00:58:06,801 --> 00:58:11,246
There is a visa issue, but I will be there by the end of next month.

662
00:58:12,418 --> 00:58:15,965
Why don't you tell us anything?

663
00:58:17,887 --> 00:58:19,160
Yoko

664
00:58:19,785 --> 00:58:21,981
What's wrong with her?

665
00:58:22,512 --> 00:58:23,317
Yoko will...

666
00:58:23,403 --> 00:58:23,903
Toki

667
00:58:24,020 --> 00:58:27,044
Let me say.
She's working now

668
00:58:28,987 --> 00:58:34,081
She is in court to separate from her and her husband.

669
00:58:34,954 --> 00:58:37,352
Are you sure,Yoko?

670
00:58:51,401 --> 00:58:57,979
I worked hard to forget you this past year

671
00:58:59,182 --> 00:59:01,229
That's also the reason why I go to Cambodia

672
00:59:02,323 --> 00:59:06,346
But the truth is, I thought of you every day.

673
00:59:07,839 --> 00:59:11,496
I thought of you every day too

674
00:59:11,941 --> 00:59:16,972
I didn't know you were suffering so much.

675
00:59:17,958 --> 00:59:22,427
I wanted to divorce Sawano on my own.

676
00:59:23,787 --> 00:59:27,217
I am trying to solve it myself

677
00:59:28,412 --> 00:59:31,826
I wanted to get back myself, Yoko Niimura, and saw you again

678
00:59:33,186 --> 00:59:37,428
I thought it was the only way I could get you to forgive me

679
00:59:39,445 --> 00:59:43,226
Yoko, don't think too much

680
00:59:45,381 --> 00:59:46,413
Mitsuharu

681
00:59:48,022 --> 00:59:50,967
I haven't changed my mind

682
00:59:52,171 --> 00:59:53,342
Me too

683
00:59:54,842 --> 00:59:55,850
I love you

684
01:00:15,223 --> 01:00:18,262
I am happy to meet you after a long time

685
01:00:19,387 --> 01:00:21,035
Be happy

686
01:00:21,684 --> 01:00:23,145
I'll support you from now on

687
01:00:32,297 --> 01:00:39,594
The complaint states that your husband SHINSUKE was unreasonable out of jealousy.

688
01:00:41,122 --> 01:00:44,817
do you know why he got jealous?

689
01:00:45,653 --> 01:00:46,325
No

690
01:00:47,192 --> 01:00:48,958
Do you know Mitsuharu Sugano?

691
01:00:50,856 --> 01:00:51,442
I know

692
01:00:51,661 --> 01:00:57,005
Last July, you visited him a lot while he was in the hospital.

693
01:00:57,635 --> 01:00:59,533
That's true

694
01:01:01,737 --> 01:01:08,760
But he had a special disease called amnesia.

695
01:01:09,516 --> 01:01:15,969
I was told by the doctor to come in for his treatment from time to time.

696
01:01:16,954 --> 01:01:23,821
I thought I could tell my husband about it and he would understand.

697
01:01:24,376 --> 01:01:29,141
If his illness is cured, you won't need to see him,right?

698
01:01:29,571 --> 01:01:29,962
No

699
01:01:30,173 --> 01:01:35,063
Have you had anything with him since last July?

700
01:01:35,368 --> 01:01:36,165
Right

701
01:01:36,376 --> 01:01:38,204
Have you never met him since then?

702
01:01:44,212 --> 01:01:49,314
You met him three days before September 15th.

703
01:01:52,635 --> 01:01:57,018
Machida 3-chome, Shinagawa-ku.
Shumpu apartment,Toki machida

704
01:01:57,784 --> 01:02:01,885
You met him and spent two hours in that room.

705
01:02:03,824 --> 01:02:08,652
You went to Shinagawa station with him and shook hands on the platform and parted.

706
01:02:10,564 --> 01:02:11,744
Objection!

707
01:02:11,994 --> 01:02:14,236
I ask her the truth

708
01:02:14,261 --> 01:02:16,299
This is a leading question

709
01:02:16,324 --> 01:02:17,369
This is no!

710
01:02:17,394 --> 01:02:18,158
Be quiet

711
01:02:19,124 --> 01:02:20,405
Keep going

712
01:02:21,999 --> 01:02:23,460
That'll be inconvenient

713
01:02:24,796 --> 01:02:25,663
I'm sorry

714
01:02:26,382 --> 01:02:33,834
I didn't know there was a detective.
It is inconvenient for me to be unfaithful

715
01:02:35,272 --> 01:02:37,600
It was not unfaithfulness

716
01:02:38,022 --> 01:02:38,944
Sorry

717
01:02:40,004 --> 01:02:43,293
you had better not see him for a while

718
01:02:44,840 --> 01:02:45,449
I see

719
01:02:48,328 --> 01:02:50,492
what will happen to me?

720
01:02:50,758 --> 01:02:53,617
you have to prove his infidelity

721
01:02:55,156 --> 01:02:57,984
We have to find the address of ASAMI, the secretary.

722
01:02:58,828 --> 01:03:00,617
Leave it to me

723
01:03:01,906 --> 01:03:06,609
If possible, I want to be by your side

724
01:03:07,258 --> 01:03:09,664
I don't care if I lose everything

725
01:03:11,476 --> 01:03:20,250
It didn't hold up well in court.
But I was very happy to meet you

726
01:03:22,751 --> 01:03:26,774
do you remember when you were a student,Yoko?

727
01:03:27,766 --> 01:03:33,649
we were full of hope

728
01:03:35,174 --> 01:03:39,471
If you win the case we'll be back

729
01:03:40,650 --> 01:03:43,947
We did not obligate ourselves to this matchmaking.

730
01:03:44,658 --> 01:03:47,353
this was a natural match

731
01:03:47,994 --> 01:03:49,627
She was glad too

732
01:03:51,789 --> 01:03:54,274
My case is not going in my favor.

733
01:03:55,493 --> 01:04:02,446
I feel so miserable when I see them

734
01:04:06,634 --> 01:04:09,688
I'm thinking of you all day long

735
01:04:10,985 --> 01:04:13,165
I'm about to go to Cambodia

736
01:04:13,590 --> 01:04:17,887
I consider this work to be rewarding..but

737
01:04:18,629 --> 01:04:23,574
I don't know what to do if your case won't work well

738
01:04:25,360 --> 01:04:29,024
I'm writing happy news today,Mitsuharu

739
01:04:30,328 --> 01:04:31,203
Asami?

740
01:04:32,055 --> 01:04:34,508
We've found her.
Your lawyer met her yesterday

741
01:04:35,698 --> 01:04:37,057
Is that true?

742
01:04:37,432 --> 01:04:44,127
I contacted her home but no response.
I found her friend and got her contact

743
01:04:45,137 --> 01:04:51,051
She was working at bar.
Kanzaki lawyer found her

744
01:04:52,505 --> 01:04:57,137
I think our case will work well

745
01:04:57,708 --> 01:05:02,059
I got express letter.
Asami will prove you?

746
01:05:02,364 --> 01:05:05,669
Kanzaki lawyer got promised with her

747
01:05:06,770 --> 01:05:09,153
Asami does not feel good about Sawano

748
01:05:09,801 --> 01:05:11,856
That is good news

749
01:05:13,466 --> 01:05:16,466
I will be in Tokyo to see you on the next court date.

750
01:05:17,067 --> 01:05:18,755
I think my lawyer will allow it.

751
01:05:19,387 --> 01:05:21,809
I'm looking forward to it

752
01:05:23,887 --> 01:05:28,341
What? telephone bill will be high?
Ok see you then

753
01:05:29,544 --> 01:05:30,614
Hold on

754
01:05:32,895 --> 01:05:35,137
Hi,I'm Chikako

755
01:05:36,442 --> 01:05:37,684
He hanged up the phone

756
01:05:38,374 --> 01:05:41,468
Witnesses must tell the truth.

757
01:05:42,397 --> 01:05:46,343
If you tell a lie, you are committing perjury.

758
01:05:51,326 --> 01:05:54,100
You speak to the presiding judge.

759
01:05:56,397 --> 01:05:59,201
Do you know Shinsuke Sawano?

760
01:05:59,858 --> 01:06:00,233
Yes

761
01:06:00,740 --> 01:06:02,506
What relationship you have with him?

762
01:06:03,390 --> 01:06:08,484
I was her secretary when I worked at Toyo metal co.

763
01:06:08,617 --> 01:06:09,625
When was it?

764
01:06:10,289 --> 01:06:13,187
It was between Feb to Oct last year

765
01:06:13,218 --> 01:06:14,195
I see

766
01:06:15,265 --> 01:06:20,414
Besides your work, you had a special relationship with him

767
01:06:21,592 --> 01:06:22,131
What?

768
01:06:22,412 --> 01:06:24,295
I mean you were his mistress

769
01:06:24,912 --> 01:06:27,076
No way

770
01:06:27,756 --> 01:06:28,342
No?

771
01:06:30,709 --> 01:06:32,865
You didn't have such a relationship?

772
01:06:35,264 --> 01:06:36,084
No

773
01:06:39,357 --> 01:06:44,607
You accompanied him on a business trip to Miyazaki last September.

774
01:06:46,396 --> 01:06:51,412
You stayed with him in a hotel for three days.

775
01:06:52,451 --> 01:06:52,967
Yes

776
01:06:53,287 --> 01:06:55,810
Besides you, Was there another co workers?

777
01:06:56,732 --> 01:06:57,974
I was only the worker

778
01:06:58,857 --> 01:07:02,138
You did nothing to do with him?

779
01:07:02,865 --> 01:07:03,685
No

780
01:07:05,604 --> 01:07:10,361
You eat and drink in the same room with him.

781
01:07:10,846 --> 01:07:12,971
I can call the maid as a witness.

782
01:07:19,176 --> 01:07:26,426
I felt lonely to eat alone, so I asked him to eat together

783
01:07:27,700 --> 01:07:30,247
There was nothing happen more than that

784
01:07:32,083 --> 01:07:39,223
I met you at bar 1 week ago, 10/3.
You told me different

785
01:07:40,868 --> 01:07:42,407
I have no idea

786
01:07:42,493 --> 01:07:43,837
You should be honest

787
01:07:44,297 --> 01:07:45,914
Witnesses must tell the truth.

788
01:07:46,212 --> 01:07:49,516
presiding judge!
He insults the witness.

789
01:07:50,071 --> 01:07:50,829
Please reject

790
01:07:52,110 --> 01:07:54,806
You watch your language.

791
01:07:55,337 --> 01:07:56,040
I get it

792
01:07:59,786 --> 01:08:01,591
What? She rejected?

793
01:08:02,497 --> 01:08:03,419
I can't believe it

794
01:08:03,833 --> 01:08:06,240
Kanzaki got in trouble

795
01:08:07,646 --> 01:08:09,130
We got in trouble

796
01:08:09,544 --> 01:08:13,130
I will go there to see her

797
01:08:13,482 --> 01:08:15,271
That's bad

798
01:08:15,630 --> 01:08:18,786
It's not convenient for you to be here.

799
01:08:19,825 --> 01:08:22,450
I'll call you when the court is over

800
01:08:25,070 --> 01:08:29,312
She looks tired.
I will ask her a few questions

801
01:08:30,773 --> 01:08:38,398
You changed your hotel 4th of your trip schedule

802
01:08:39,229 --> 01:08:39,721
Yes

803
01:08:40,362 --> 01:08:41,018
Why?

804
01:08:41,369 --> 01:08:45,018
Niimua asked me to change my hotel

805
01:08:46,244 --> 01:08:51,526
Did you know Yoko Sawano visited him that day?

806
01:08:51,979 --> 01:08:53,237
I found out it later

807
01:08:53,588 --> 01:08:56,518
You didn't meet her that day?

808
01:08:57,642 --> 01:08:58,252
No

809
01:08:58,759 --> 01:09:00,838
She backed in Tokyo,not saw her

810
01:09:01,853 --> 01:09:04,119
I met her

811
01:09:04,322 --> 01:09:05,088
When?

812
01:09:06,103 --> 01:09:08,306
Next day the morning

813
01:09:08,494 --> 01:09:09,908
Damn it.
She was bought up

814
01:09:11,654 --> 01:09:13,436
Oh morning.
Around what time?

815
01:09:14,318 --> 01:09:16,475
Around 5 am

816
01:09:16,795 --> 01:09:19,381
It was too early.
Why?

817
01:09:20,286 --> 01:09:22,068
I just walked around

818
01:09:23,255 --> 01:09:24,802
Then you met her?

819
01:09:27,068 --> 01:09:28,638
She was alone?

820
01:09:29,310 --> 01:09:30,154
No

821
01:09:30,427 --> 01:09:32,044
With her husband?

822
